<measure quantity="4" unit="chapters">
<num value="4">四</num>卷</measure>
<pc>（</pc>江蘇巡撫采進本<pc>）</pc>國朝張先嶽撰<pc>。</pc>先岳字北拱<pc>，</pc>晉江人<pc>。</pc>是書<num value="1">一</num>名<pc>《</pc>
